Plexura: Modern Web Solutions
Plexura is the official digital home and showcase of our full-stack web design agency. This repository houses a high-performance, visually immersive platform built to demonstrate the intersection of sophisticated design and scalable architecture.

The application is engineered with the MERN stack, prioritizing a seamless user experience through fluid animations and a mobile-first philosophy.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js with Framer Motion for high-fidelity animations and Tailwind CSS for streamlined, responsive styling.

Backend: Node.js & Express.js handling robust API routing and server-side logic.

Database: MongoDB for flexible, document-based data management.

Deployment: Optimized for modern cloud environments with a focus on CI/CD best practices.

🚀 Key Features
Interactive UI: Dynamic components powered by Framer Motion to create a premium, "luxury-tech" feel.

Full-Stack Integration: A custom-built backend to manage client inquiries, project portfolios, and agency service listings.

Performance Optimized: Clean code architecture ensuring fast load times and SEO-friendly rendering.

Plexura is dedicated to bridging the gap between complex technical requirements and intuitive digital branding.
